<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
      <hr>

      <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.png", width: 200, alt: 'profile-pic', class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>


      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>With no hope in sight and a journey going nowhere I needed to feel alive once again. Living in the land of opportunity and even better Silicon Valley, why not make a life breaking decision that would alter yet enhance the rest of my life?</p>

        <p>For this reason I decided to focus my efforts...</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='jobHistory'
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='education'
          >
            Education
          </button>

        </p>
        <p>

          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>

